<header>
	Read the writing task on the left and answer the questions on the right. In some cases, there is more than one correct answer.
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000"><b>1.</b>  Who do you have to write to?</font>
    <g id="t1">A. your boss</g>
    <g id="t2">B. a colleague</g>
    <g id="t3">C. a stranger</g>
    <g id="t4">D. a friend</g>
    <g id="t5">E. a relative</g>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000"><b>2.</b>  What style of letter should you write?</font>
    <g id="t6">A. formal</g>
    <g id="t7">B. informal</g>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000"><b>3.</b>  What do you have to do in this letter?</font>
    <g id="t8">A. make an apology</g>
    <g id="t9">B. make an application</g>
    <g id="t10">C. make a complaint</g>
    <g id="t11">D. request action</g>
    <g id="t12">E. make arrangements</g>
  </p>
  <p align="left"><font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000"><b>4.</b>  How many points do you have to</font>cover in this letter?<g id="t13">A. one</g><g id="t14">B. two</g><g id="t15">C. three</g><g id="t16">D. four</g><g id="t17">E. five</g></p>
  <p align="left"><font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000"><b>5.</b>  Which of the following could you write</font>about in this letter?<g id="t18">A. the colour of the rubbish bins</g><g id="t19">B. the sight of the rubbish bins</g><g id="t20">C. the smell of the rubbish bins</g><g id="t21">D. the noise during the collection of the rubbish</g><g id="t22">E. the view from the hotel windows</g><g id="t23">F. the mess left after the collection of the rubbish</g><g id="t24">G. the smell the collection of the rubbish creates</g><g id="t25">H. the loss of business for the hotel due to the smell of rubbish</g></p>
