<section id="readingText">
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#0000ff">
      <b>Writing Task 1</b>
    </font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">You should spend about 20 minutes on this task.</p>
  <p align="left">
    <b>You live next to a large hotel. The hotel's rubbish bins are kept directly below your bedroom window and this is causing you problems.</b>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <b>Write a letter to the hotel. Explain how you are being affected by this situation and say what you would like them to do about it.</b>
  </p>
  <p align="left">You should write at least 150 words.</p>
  <p align="left">You do <b>NOT</b> need to write your own address.</p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">Begin your letter as follows:</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">Dear Sir/Madam, </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font size="2"/>
  </p>
